      "message": "This is all un-needed code if someone has not enabled the meson option, persist-settings-to-file, but it\u0027s also basically a noop if someone doesn\u0027t have the feature enabled. We\u0027ll see if anyone else weighs in on whether the signal handling should be wrapped behind that meson option.",
